{"tid":2161171,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【華為危機】羅馬尼亞5G拒用受懷疑公司 華使館兩斥美搞局欺凌","createTime":"2020-08-17T11:55:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-17T12:01:04.000Z","uid":36494,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"268ae1438d109c0b944fe30566e14bd9fda6cd9d","tid":2161171,"uid":36494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T11:55:51.000Z","msg":"美國連番追擊中國電訊設備製造商華為，再有一歐洲國家表態支持。羅馬尼亞日前公佈5G網絡立法草案，提出了網絡設備供應商應符合的條件，相關官員更明言，要防止某些受人懷疑的公司進入當地5G市場。中國駐羅馬尼亞大使館本月二度就5G問題發聲，狠批美國到處脅迫盟友排斥華為，「這是赤裸裸的霸凌行徑和政治操弄。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20200817/4N2I4ZRPWNB2XEUPPWYVO5BTTY/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200817%2F4N2I4ZRPWNB2XEUPPWYVO5BTTY%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&d=hvnZYtOEdtVTkBm9e3s21B6eP3a%2FjAUraAi1lUB%2B7iI%3D&h=c79d11a0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200817%2F4N2I4ZRPWNB2XEUPPWYVO5BTTY%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&h=c2ce5f31\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20200817/4N2I4ZRPWNB2XEUPPWYVO5BTTY/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post</a>"},{"pid":"652998c5eb6d995338dd328f2716195b73ccb176","tid":2161171,"uid":343361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T11:57:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6501e2e451459f37ac5b7f13f80e7de413d09f70","tid":2161171,"uid":53379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T11:57:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有後門 不了"},{"pid":"e0570d2b48d7c0e22fbd3b61fab56e481aa639a3","tid":2161171,"uid":214502,